      "text": [
        "هِمْ مَنْ هُوَ أَعْلَمُ مِنْهُ لَمْ يَزَلْ أَمْرُهُمْ إِلَى سَفَالٍ إِلَى يَوْمِ اَلْقِيَامَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1102 - The Messenger of Allah (sw) said:\n\"Whoever leads a people in prayer while there is someone among them who is more knowledgeable than him, their affairs will continue to decline until the Day of Judgment.\""
        ]
